{"tid":2298399,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍韜文：港逼公僕宣誓或違聯合聲明","createTime":"2020-11-24T04:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T05:23:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6d72ea2bd9abad2ad38374c99c7f1eb927bda7e3","tid":2298399,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/WUKTCEIJQRHUZMRCTZB4HWPQ2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FWUKTCEIJQRHUZMRCTZB4HWPQ2M%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaKof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=ebb80445\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FWUKTCEIJQRHUZMRCTZB4HWPQ2M%2F&h=f5488856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/WUKTCEIJQRHUZMRCTZB4HWPQ2M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文：港逼公僕宣誓或違聯合聲明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aY84MAZThNPkHP65SA73dWDlGhU=/1736x977/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GIMDBZFGBNBQTHT4BCVI74D3KE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaY84MAZThNPkHP65SA73dWDlGhU%3D%2F1736x977%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGIMDBZFGBNBQTHT4BCVI74D3KE.jpg&h=8cfd4839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■藍韜文提交香港半年報告，轟中國違反聯合聲明。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【香港半年報告】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 英國外相藍韜文向國會提交最新的香港半年報告，指中國對港實施國安法，嚴重違反中英聯合聲明，英國政府除了「BNO5+1」方案外，還會延長對港警備禁運，藍韜文亦與英國大法官正在商討，是否仍適合讓英國法官來港任終審法院非常任法官，更首次提及關注港府要求公務員宣誓效忠事件，有否違反中英聯合聲明中公務員任命及晉升原則。<br />\n<br />\n該份半份報告長29頁，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延續禁運鎮壓工具<br />\n<br />\n報告又列出多項侵蝕自由和人權事件，包括有人提倡以「愛國教育」取代通識科、中史取消試題事件，以及圖書館書籍審查政治內容，更特別用粗體字列出，留意到公務員在國安法生效後要宣誓，而之前港府就是用宣誓來DQ民主派議員，英方關注宣誓有否違反中英聯合聲明，有關公務員任命和晉升的原則，又提及立法會內會風波，以致政府DQ議員和押後選舉、禁止人權組織入境，以及國安法被用作搜查報館和拘捕媒體老闆手段，香港警察亦恐嚇叫口號和舉標語的示威市民等。<br />\n<br />\n報告總結中國沒有履行國際承諾，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，不斷利用法律作為利器去控制和駕馭人民，無視社會不公義問題，香港最終都是難長治久安。"},{"pid":"5f45688ccf7c97f3bda0a4dc5663572bc83f7214","tid":2298399,"uid":221343,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"又違聯合聲明...違反又點？冇後果點解要怕違反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2664a41520c6b27d892d2767286ce6b252990c1","tid":2298399,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f45688ccf7c97f3bda0a4dc5663572bc83f7214","tid":2298399,"uid":221343,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"又違聯合聲明...違反又點？冇後果點解要怕違反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"冇得5+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ba2382cf1aea0e4a5bcdd435aee9ad70ee0116","tid":2298399,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f45688ccf7c97f3bda0a4dc5663572bc83f7214","tid":2298399,"uid":221343,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"又違聯合聲明...違反又點？冇後果點解要怕違反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"架船下年先到<br />\n即係就算違反都仲有成年要受"},{"pid":"91b8accf6f6c84015705ee680096cd88bd004032","tid":2298399,"uid":305358,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"入得去做公墓員就預咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843a202e8a5e4c4c80dddd8467ad657467ecde6a","tid":2298399,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"香港政府表示聯合聲明只係歷史文件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afed3c9c07d9752596924bf6fc4098bb498dad4","t